{"tid":1549991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"機管局：全日機場運作及航班升降正常","createTime":"2019-09-07T13:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:47:33.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae3c483397ef0bceeca15af33ce2826940273e6","tid":1549991,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T13:47:33.000Z","msg":"網上有人號召今日阻塞來往機場的交通。機管局表示，啟動了機場緊急應變中心，協調機場運作，全日機場運作及航班升降運作一直維持正常。<br />\n<br />\n機管局今日曾根據機管局附例，要求一些人士離開機管局附例適用區。此外，下午部分人士於機場地面運輸中心聚集，機管局配合執達主任及警方執行臨時禁制令，要求這些人離開機場。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2245208/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2245208%2F&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uOzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=17b76cbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2245208/</a>"}]}